{"slug":"a-new-life","title":{"en":"A New Life","km":"ជីវិតនិងអនាគត"},"description":{"en":" Yam Chi Ho, raised in the triads and frequently imprisoned, is temporarily released to attend his father's funeral. Monitored by the police, he feels immense pressure. He meets social worker Ha Ching Man, who helps guide him toward reform. However, when Chi Ho's actions lead to a miscarriage for his wife, Pui Kuen, she leaves him. Despite his guilt, Ching Man encourages him to change.\n","km":" យ៉ាំ ជីហូ ដែលធំធាត់ក្នុងគ្រួសារបីនាក់ ហើយតែងតែជាប់ពន្ធនាគារ ត្រូវបានដោះលែងជាបណ្ដោះអាសន្នដើម្បីចូលរួមពិធីបុណ្យសពឪពុករបស់គាត់។ ដោយមានការត្រួតពិនិត្យពីប៉ូលីស គាត់មានអារម្មណ៍ថាមានសម្ពាធយ៉ាងខ្លាំង។ គាត់បានជួបជាមួយអ្នកសង្គមកិច្ច ហា ឈីង ម៉ាន់ ដែលជួយណែនាំគាត់ឆ្ពោះទៅរកការកែទម្រង់។ ទោះជាយ៉ាងណាក៏ដោយ នៅពេលដែលសកម្មភាពរបស់ ជីហូ នាំឱ្យភរិយារបស់គាត់ គឺ ពូយ គួន រលូតកូន នាងបានចាកចេញពីគាត់។ ទោះបីជាមានកំហុសក៏ដោយ ឈីង ម៉ាន់ លើកទឹកចិត្តគាត់ឱ្យផ្លាស់ប្តូរ។"},"poster":"https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BNjA0ZDI2M2QtZDY0Yi00ZTZiLTk1ZDEtMDFiNTcyNTc2ZWMxXkEyXkFqcGc@._V1_.jpg","year":1991,"rating":8.1,"genres":["ACTION","COMEDY","DRAMA","HORROR","FANTASY","THRILLER","ROMANCE"],"language":"English","episodeCount":15,"episodes":[{"ep":"1","title":{"en":"Episode 1","km":"ភាគទី1"},"url":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/iamcleanerkak/yai/refs/heads/i1/x/index.single","type":"M3U8","final":false},{"ep":"2","title":{"en":"Episode 2","km":"ភាគទី2"},"url":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/iamcleanerkak/yai/refs/heads/i2/x/index.single","type":"M3U8","final":false},{"ep":"3","title":{"en":"Episode 3","km":"ភាគទី3"},"url":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/iamcleanerkak/yai/refs/heads/i3/x/index.single","type":"M3U8","final":false},{"ep":"4","title":{"en":"Episode 4","km":"ភាគទី4"},"url":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/iamcleanerkak/yai/refs/heads/i4/x/index.single","type":"M3U8","final":false},{"ep":"5","title":{"en":"Episode 5","km":"ភាគទី5"},"url":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/iamcleanerkak/yai/refs/heads/